<HEADLINE>
ABC DISPUTES DRUG OFFICE CLAIMS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients, also moved on the ``n''
California and ``e'' entertainment news wires.) 
By Valerie Kuklenski  
 c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
