Saturday with some of his 1983 fifth-grade students from Sherwood
Elementary in Highland Park, at a recent class reunion. From left,
are Alison Gordon, Stacey Solomon and Jo Ann Fiore. Seventeen years
ago, Berg asked the 27 students in his fifth-grade class, ages 10
