<P>
   In response to the belt-tightening, last year Michelin
introduced a new category, ``Bib Gourmand,'' consisting of
restaurants that offer good meals and good value.
</P>
<P>
   As always, the guide thrives by subtly reflecting the shifting
fortunes of France herself. &QL; 
